a string which is the name of an existing
		environment variable;
		case-sensitive

a string which is the name of a new or existing
		environment variable;
		case-sensitive

zero if the function call completes successfully;
		otherwise, a platform-dependent integer which describes
		the problem

refsect1.para:
Looks up the current working directory of the &CCL; process;
unless it has been changed, this is the directory &CCL; was
started in.

